Subject: watchdog: allow building BCM7038_WDT for BCM4908
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: cd91fb2776967b2b2dea27307a3f23ba3d9bbb32
Patch-mainline: v5.18-rc1
References: bsc#1208619

BCM4908 is a SoCs family that shares a lot of hardware with BCM63xx
including the watchdog block. Allow building this driver for it.

